The paper discusses the risks and threats arising from the usage of ICT techniques in smart environments, with emphasis on networking. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cyber-physical systems (cs.CY). The paper also considers the human aspects of security and privacy, which could be related to social and information sciences (cs.SI), software engineering (cs.SE), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
